{
  "prompt": "A combined sacred sigil merging the divine feminine archetypes of Sophia and Lilith. The sigil should blend elements of wisdom (Sophia) such as a stylized owl, a crown, or an open eye, with Lilith’s symbolism—such as a crescent moon, serpents, wings, and a dark flame. The design should be symmetrical, elegant yet powerful, etched in light and shadow, with a mystical, ancient appearance. Background should be dark or translucent to highlight the luminous details of the sigil.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A powerful golden sigil combining Metatron and Samael archetypes: a hexagram interlaced with a serpent-entwined sword, surrounded by wings of fire and sacred geometry. The upper section features an eye within a cube (Metatron's Cube), while the lower half is flanked by shadowy serpents and a flaming double-edged blade. The entire sigil glows against a dark, textured background, evoking angelic and infernal power united in balance.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}
